pageContext.claim: “Actually, there were two conversations [with Zelensky]. The first one was ‘Hello,’ ‘Goodbye.’ They don't even talk about that. The second one was about the same thing.”
pageContext.analysis: The first phone conversation between Trump and Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky was as he says. But the second one was much different. Trump asked Zelensky to dig up political dirt on Joe Biden and investigate a conspiracy theory that Ukrainians and not Russians interfered in the 2016 U.S. election.
